high_descs: Turn around, take a few steps forward, turn left towards the stove, and then turn right to walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into three pieces.
Set the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Turn right and head to the fridge on your left.
Place the apple in the fridge for it to cool and then take it back out.
Turn around, walk to the window, turn right to the door, and then turn right to find a black bin on the floor.
Place the apple piece in the black bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled slice of apple in the black bin.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the fridge, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife out of the sink.
Slice up the apple in the sink into three pieces.
Put the butter knife down in the sink.
Pick up one of the apple slices out of the sink.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the apple slice inside then close the fridge door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the apple slice, then close the fridge door.
Turn around and start walking across the room, then turn right and walk over to the door, turn right to face the counter.
Put the chilled apple slice in the black bin in the ground.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled apple slice in a black bin.

high_descs: Turn around and veer left to the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Use the knife to cut the apple in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink to the left of the spatula.
Pick up one of the slices of apple.
Turn right and walk to the fridge.
Place the piece of apple in the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and take the apple out again.
Turn around and walk straight and right around the counter to the bin next to the yellow chairs.
Place the piece of apple in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled, cut piece of apple in a trash bin.
